<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="yes" HEAD="rel-pron" CASE="nominative">who himself</REFEX>
</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 (pronounced Oiler; IPA [IPA: [ˈɔʏlɐ]]) (Basel, Switzerland, April 15, 1707 - St Petersburg, Russia, September 18, 1783) was a Swiss mathematician and physicist.
</PARAGRAPH>

<PARAGRAPH>
<REF ID="1635.2" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="np-subj">
